<subSubSection id="2DF0ACA1FFF9FFC5FF71F885FE4BFF7B" lastPageId="18" lastPageNumber="19" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" type="description">
<paragraph id="6555FF2AFFF9FFC6FF71F885FDBEF8DF" blockId="17.[151,1437,1842,2013]" box="[151,579,1878,1905]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
(
<figureCitation id="FDD1E3AFFFF9FFC6FF79F885FF0BF8DF" box="[159,246,1879,1905]" captionStart="FIGURE 11" captionStartId="64.[151,250,1965,1989]" captionTargetBox="[195,1391,191,1929]" captionTargetId="figure-32@64.[189,1399,181,1941]" captionTargetPageId="64" captionText="FIGURE 11. Eudocima kuehni and Eudocima cocalus group adults (dorsal aspect)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6605524" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6605524/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Figs 11</figureCitation>
: C–E, 20: B–C, 25: K, 31: K)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6555FF2AFFF9FFC5FF71F8A9FE4BFF7B" blockId="17.[151,1437,1842,2013]" lastBlockId="18.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="18" lastPageNumber="19" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FF71F8A9FE95F83B" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1777" box="[151,360,1915,1941]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cocalus">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFF9FFC6FF71F8A9FE95F83B" box="[151,360,1915,1941]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Eudocima cocalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FE45F8A9FDA3F83B" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1780" box="[419,606,1915,1941]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hypermnestra">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFF9FFC6FE45F8A9FDA3F83B" box="[419,606,1915,1941]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">E. hypermnestra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
doubtfully represent separate species as discussed above. 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FB18F8A9FF2FF817" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1777" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cocalus">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFF9FFC6FB18F8A9FF2FF817" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Eudocima cocalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
lacks paired black medial spots on the hindwing which are present in 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FC3BF84DFB6BF817" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1780" box="[989,1174,1951,1977]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hypermnestra">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFF9FFC6FC3BF84DFB6BF817" box="[989,1174,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">E. hypermnestra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FB45F84DFA8CF817" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1777" box="[1187,1393,1951,1977]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cocalus">
<emphasis id="579E2338FFF9FFC6FB45F84DFA8CF817" box="[1187,1393,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Eudocima cocalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a less dentate inner margin of the dorsal hindwing marginal band relative to 
<emphasis id="579E2338FFF9FFC6FBE4F811FA60F873" box="[1026,1437,1987,2013]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FBE4F811FB3CF873" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1780" box="[1026,1217,1987,2013]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hypermnestra">E. hypermnestra</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName id="A2EA84A9FFF9FFC6FB2BF811FA60F873" baseAuthorityName="Cramer" baseAuthorityYear="1777" box="[1229,1437,1987,2013]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Eudocima" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cocalus">Eudocima cocalus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is widely distributed from the Sunda Islands and the 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFFAFFC5FD13FF45FC8EFF1F" box="[757,883,151,177]" name="Philippines" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Philippines</collectingCountry>
east to New 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFFAFFC5FBEAFF45FB9DFF1F" box="[1036,1120,151,177]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Guinea</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFFAFFC5FB8AFF45FB2EFF1F" box="[1132,1235,151,177]" name="Australia" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Australia</collectingCountry>
and the 
<collectingCountry id="1DFDBFBAFFFAFFC5FAD1FF45FF1BFF7B" name="Solomon Islands" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Solomon Islands</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="017B82DBFFFAFFC5FF13FF69FE57FF7B" author="Zilli, A. &amp; Brou, V. A. &amp; Klem, C. &amp; Zaspel, J." box="[245,426,187,213]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" pagination="152 - 166" refId="ref41849" refString="Zilli, A., Brou, V. A., Klem, C. &amp; Zaspel, J. (2017) The Eudocima Billberg, 1820 of the Australian Region (Lepidoptera: Erebidae). In: Telnov, D. (Ed.), Biodiversity, Biogeography and Nature Conservation in Wallacea and New Guinea. Vol. 3. The Entomological Society of Latvia, Riga, pp. 631 - 655, pls. 152 - 166." type="book chapter" year="2017">
Zilli 
<emphasis id="579E2338FFFAFFC5FEC8FF69FEA2FF7B" box="[302,351,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">et al</emphasis>
. 2017
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
